#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:5
msgid "random numbers"
msgstr "random numbers"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:9
msgid ""
"When one wishes to specify a large but random number of things, and the "
"context is inappropriate for :ref:`N`\\, certain numbers are preferred by "
"hacker tradition (that is, easily recognized as placeholders). These include"
" the following:"
msgstr ""
"大きいが任意の数のものを指定したいとき、その文脈が\\ :ref:`N`\\ "
"にふさわしくない場合、ハッカーの伝統によって特定の数が好まれる(つまり、プレースホルダーとして容易に認識される)。それには以下が含まれる。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:14
msgid "17"
msgstr "17"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:15
msgid ""
"Long described at MIT as ‘the least random number’; see also 23. This may be"
" Discordian in origin, or it may be related to some in-jokes about `17 and "
"yellowpig <http://www.vinc17.org/yp17_eng.html>`_\\  propagated by the "
"mathematician Michael Spivak."
msgstr ""
"MITで長らく‘最も乱数らしくない数’と評されてきた。23も参照。これはディスコルディアン起源かもしれないし、数学者Michael "
"Spivakによって広められた\\ `17 and yellowpig "
"<http://www.vinc17.org/yp17_eng.html>`_\\ にまつわる内輪のジョークに関係しているのかもしれない。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:17
msgid "23"
msgstr "23"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:18
msgid "Sacred number of Eris, Goddess of Discord (along with 17 and 5)."
msgstr "不和の女神エリスの神聖な数(17と5とともに)。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:19
msgid "37"
msgstr "37"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:20
msgid ""
"The most random two-digit number is 37, When groups of people are polled to "
"pick a \"random number between 1 and 100\", the most commonly chosen number "
"is 37."
msgstr "最も乱数らしい二桁の数は37である。人々のグループに「1から100までの乱数」を選ぶよう尋ねると、最も多く選ばれる数は37だ。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:21
msgid "42"
msgstr "42"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:22
msgid ""
"The Answer to the Ultimate Question of Life, the Universe, and Everything "
"(\"what is 6 times 9\", correct in base 13). (This answer is perhaps not "
"completely fortuitous; in Kabbalism, the true unspeakable name of God is "
"said to have 42 characters.)"
msgstr ""
"生命、宇宙、そして万物についての究極の問いへの答え(「6かける9は何か」、13進法で正しい)。(この答えはおそらく完全に偶然というわけではない。カバラでは、神の真の口にしてはならない名は42文字あるとされている。)"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:24
msgid "69"
msgstr "69"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:25
msgid "From the sexual act. This one was favored in MIT's ITS culture."
msgstr "性行為から。これはMITのITS文化で好まれた。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:27
msgid "105"
msgstr "105"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:28
msgid "69 hex = 105 decimal, and 69 decimal = 105 octal."
msgstr "16進数の69は10進数の105、10進数の69は8進数の105である。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:29
msgid "666"
msgstr "666"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:30
msgid "In Christian mythology, the Number of the Beast."
msgstr "キリスト教神話における獣の数字。"

#: ../../R/random-numbers.rst:32
msgid ""
"For further enlightenment, study the *Principia Discordia*\\, * The "
"Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy*\\, *The Joy of Sex*\\, and the Christian "
"Bible (Revelation 13:18). See also :ref:`Discordianism` or consult your "
"pineal gland. See also :ref:`for-values-of`\\."
msgstr ""
"さらなる啓蒙のためには、『Principia Discordia』(\\ *Principia Discordia*\\)、『The "
"Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy』(\\ * The Hitchhiker's Guide to the "
"Galaxy*\\)、『The Joy of Sex』(\\ *The Joy of "
"Sex*\\)、そしてキリスト教の聖書(ヨハネの黙示録13章18節)を研究せよ。\\ :ref:`Discordianism`\\ "
"も参照、あるいは自分の松果体に相談せよ。\\ :ref:`for-values-of`\\ も参照。"
